data.description: Elegant, 1-acre property located in the serene, hidden gem neighborhood of “Country Meadows” . With a total of 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, this spacious home is over 4800 total square feet. Equipped with an exceptionally large primary bedroom with a 5 piece ensuite bathroom. Open main floor features a gourmet kitchen overlooking the family room. The formal dining room is exceptional for entertaining anywhere from large get togethers to grand family dinners. This home also boasts Hickory wood floors, newer interior paint through-out , a 4 car attached garage and a front circle drive-way. The Large loft area upstairs is perfect for any of your flex space needs. The unfinished garden level basement floods with natural light throughout the day giving way for endless possibilities to finish as you please. Lush exterior landscaping and enough space for any and all of your summer day activities. Equipped with 2 AC units. The septic system has been recently pumped and inspected and the roof and fence have been recently replaced and are brand new. This property shares a zip w/ Frederick as technically this property is in Erie and located in the Erie school districts, located on west side on I-25
